>> time required: 1 hours
>> course: entree

Peel and slice @carrots{225%g} into matchsticks and place in bowl
Place chopped @garlic cloves{4}, @sichuan peppercorns{30}, and slied @dried red chilies{4} on carrots
Heat @oil{60%ml} until smoking.
Pour oil over carrots and aromatics
Add @salt{1/2%tsp}, @sugar{1%tsp}, @sesame oil{4%tsp}, and @white vinegar{60%ml} to bowl and mix
Garnish with @cilantro{1}
